title: Christian McBride - Latin Jazz
description:
Christian McBride was exposed to Latin jazz at a young age when his father played bass with Mongo Santamaría. The fusion of different cultures struck him deeply and led him to explore the history and subtext of Latin jazz. In this video, he recounts the story of playing with legend Eddie Palmieri, an honor for any jazz musician!
